05c9f6-570a-48ed-962f-3b9a2a4ea51f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20AI-powered%20tracking%20systems%20can%20boost%20customer%20satisfaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFourKites%20taps%20into%20Bayer's%20transportation-management%20system%2C%20data%20that%20shows%20which%20goods%20are%20assigned%20to%20various%20carriers%20along%20the%20supply%20chain.%20By%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emachine-learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-artificial-intelligence-is-changing-everyday-technology-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial-intelligence%20algorithms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bayer%20has%20seen%20an%20improvement%20in%20prediction%20quality%20of%20about%2048%25%20throughout%20an%20ocean%20journey%2C%20FourKites%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20FourKites%20has%20also%20used%20generative%20AI%20to%20allow%20customers%20such%20as%20Bayer%20to%20ask%20AI%20chatbots%20questions%20about%20their%20logistics%20and%20what%20disruptions%20like%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapse%20may%20mean%20for%20them.%20The%20bots%20can%20even%20make%20recommendations%20on%20how%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriya%20Rajagopalan%2C%20the%20president%20of%20product%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20operations%20at%20FourKites%2C%20said%20the%20company%20launched%20more%20than%20eight%20years%20ago%20to%20give%20shipping%20visibility%20to%20large%20shippers%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20customers%20can%20easily%20track%20their%20orders%20via%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourKites%20tracks%20more%20than%203%20million%20shipments%20daily%20across%20roads%2C%20rails%2C%20the%20ocean%2C%20and%20air%2C%20reaching%20over%20200%20countries%20and%20territories%20and%20giving%20companies%20like%20Walmart%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20Kraft%20Heinz%20better%20visibility%20into%20when%20the%20goods%20they%20produce%20will%20be%20delivered%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22417d810c-87c2-4b21-bf0d-5a8d5f5666ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonitoring%20complex%20ocean%20shipments%20to%20avoid%20supply-chain%20disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supply-chain%20disruptions%20from%20the%20pandemic%20led%20to%20great%20interest%20from%20large%20food%20and%20beverage%20companies%20to%20more%20closely%20track%20shipments%2C%20especially%20those%20moving%20across%20the%20ocean%2C%20which%20hadn't%20previously%20been%20as%20big%20of%20a%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20the%20disruption%20was%20so%20large%20that%20just%20the%20fact%20that%20nobody%20is%20monitoring%20it%20and%20they%20have%20no%20tech%20around%20it%20became%20such%20a%20point%20of%20vulnerability%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajagopalan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20almost%20every%20chief%20supply-chain%20officer%20received%20the%20mandate%20that%20we%20cannot%20have%20these%20sorts%20of%20blind%20spots%20and%20areas%20of%20vulnerability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20FourKites%20focused%20on%20providing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-mile-delivery-shipping-explained%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal-time%20visibility%20for%20shipments%20on%20trucks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20highly%20fragmented%20system%20with%20over%203%20million%20trucks%20handled%20by%20over%20half%20a%20million%20carriers%20on%20US%20roads%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seas%20have%20seen%20more%20high-profile%20disruptions%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20a%20container%20ship%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimeline-and-pictures-of-the-ever-given-stuck-suez-canal-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estuck%20in%20the%20Suez%20Canal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouthi-iran-navy-red-sea-military-suez-yemen-israel-palestine-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%20Yemen%20Houthi%20rebel%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%20These%20challenges%20have%20led%20more%20large%20multinational%20conglomerates%20to%20work%20with%20FourKites%20to%20predict%20more%20accurately%20when%20their%20shipments%20will%20arrive%20in%20ports.%20This%20information%20is%20of%20particular%20interest%20to%20industries%20such%20as%20farming%20and%20fashion%2C%20both%20reliant%20on%20specific%20windows%20of%20seasonality%20to%20achieve%20maximum%20sales%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourKites'%20machine-learning%20algorithms%20have%20helped%20Bayer%20predict%20the%20time%20of%20arrival%20of%20ocean%20shipments%20within%20two%20days%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20insights%20can%20help%20influence%20decisions%20along%20the%20full%20supply-chain%20journey.%20For%20example%2C%20think%20of%20a%20storm%20brewing%20outside%20Japan%20that's%20disrupting%20shipments%20of%20raw%20agricultural%20materials%20meant%20for%20delivery%20to%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20think%20a%20couple%20steps%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBayer%20would%20get%20an%20alert%20from%20FourKites%2C%20which%20would%20then%20help%20influence%20a%20few%20key%20decisions.%20Knowing%20that%20a%20shipment%20is%20delayed%20across%20the%20ocean%2C%20Bayer%20may%20need%20to%20plan%20for%20congestion%20at%20the%20port.%20Now%2C%20a%20delivery%20that%20was%20intended%20for%20the%20first%20week%20of%20June%20won't%20come%20until%20a%20week%20later.%20Knowing%20this%2C%20Bayer%20could%20have%20its%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20Iowa%20readjust%20its%20production-line%20planning%20to%20account%20for%20the%20delayed%20deliveries%2C%20instead%20focusing%20on%20making%20products%20with%20the%20goods%20it%20has%20on%20hand%20from%20other%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tracking%20system%20also%20allows%20Bayer%20sales%20representatives%20to%20know%20when%20the%20seeds%20will%20be%20delivered%20to%20the%20farmer%20in%20Illinois.%20Previously%2C%20that%20representative%20would%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20someone%20in%20customer%20service%2C%20who%20would%20then%20call%20logistics%20and%20then%20call%20the%20carrier%20to%20get%20intel%20on%20disruptions.%20Now%2C%20all%20that%20information%20is%20available%20virtually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%2C%20you%20are%20feeding%20into%20this%20kind%20of%20intelligence%20that%20I%20think%20is%20getting%20better%20and%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716394550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66464a819fc063e829b1e5c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayer%20implemented%20FourKites'%20AI-powered%20real-time%20tracking%20in%202021%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20time-sensitive%20domestic%20and%20global%20shipments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20Kell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marvel%20Sets%20Vision%20Series%20for%202026%20With%20Paul%20Bettany%2C%20%E2%80%98Star%20Trek%3A%20Picard%E2%80%99%20EP%20Terry%20Matalas%20as%20Showrunner%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716394500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FVision-Matalas.jpg%3Fcrop%3D0px%252C0px%252C1200px%252C675px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236003735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marvel%20has%20tapped%2