0Revanna)%20will%20come%20back....%20Don't%20take%20advice%20from%20any%20advocates%20on%20this%20matter.%20To%20save%20his%20morality%20he%20has%20to%20come%20back%20from%20wherever%20he%20is%2C%20this%20is%20my%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20another%20query%2C%20he%20said%20Mr%20Revanna%20was%20neither%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20father%20and%20MLA%20H%20D%20Revanna%20nor%20with%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20will%20I%20go%20search%20for%20him%3F%20If%20I%20go%20abroad%2C%20they%20will%20say%20I%20have%20gone%20to%20save%20Prajwal...%20he%20is%20not%20in%20contact%20with%20anyone%2C%20with%20the%20advice%20of%20some%20advocates%20all%20these%20things%20have%20happened.%20In%20case%2C%20I%20had%20come%20to%20know%20about%20him%20leaving%20for%20abroad%20on%20April%2027%2C%20I%20would%20have%20stopped%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrajwal%20had%20sought%20a%20week's%20time%20to%20appear%20before%20SIT%2C%20but%20it%20was%20denied%20and%20another%20rape%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20him.%20With%20all%20this%20he%20might%20be%20afraid%20(to%20come%20back)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20reports%20that%20some%20businessman%20was%20helping%20Mr%20Revanna%2C%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20aware%20of%20it.%20No%20businessman%20comes%20to%20me%2C%20only%20people%20wanting%20to%20share%20their%20difficulties%20come%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20planned%20to%20finish%20off%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20family%20politically%2C%20with%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716393600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8924j0d8_hd-kumaraswamy_625x300_05_Apri