20any%20money%2C%20just%20a%20few%20seconds%20of%20their%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Tilbury%2C%20a%20TikTok%20content%20creator%20with%20seven%20million%20followers%20who%20makes%20videos%20about%20money%20and%20success%2C%20told%20BI%20Gen%20Zerz%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20smart%20with%20money%20and%20have%20noticed%20that%20%26quot%3Bhelping%20each%20other%20is%20the%20key%20to%20financial%20success.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20incredible%20to%20see%20how%20much%20TikTok%20has%20evolved%20as%20a%20platform%20and%20how%20much%20they're%20investing%20in%20rewarding%20their%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20RPMs%20aren't%20always%20ideal%2C%20they're%20better%20than%20many%20other%20apps.%20So%20anyone%20with%20a%20phone%20should%20jump%20on%20this%20opportunity%20to%20make%20extra%20money%20through%20TikTok.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVarbanova%20told%20BI%20it%20can%20be%20so%20effective%20thanks%20to%20the%20unique%20way%20TikTok%20pushes%20out%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20on%20Instagram%2C%20or%20Facebook%2C%20or%20YouTube%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20only%20something%20you%20can%20do%20on%20TikTok%20because%20of%20the%20unique%20TikTok%20algorithm.%20It%20prioritizes%20videos%20that%20have%20been%20proven%20to%20be%20watched%20all%20the%20way%20until%20the%20end%20by%20a%20group%20of%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20aren't%20influencers%20trying%20to%20sell%20something%20or%20companies%20asking%20for%20money%2C%20she%20said.%20They%20are%20regular%20people%20encouraging%20each%20other%20to%20help%20by%20giving%20up%20a%20minute%20of%20their%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20tides%20on%20social%20media%20can%20turn%20quickly%2C%20Varbanova%20added%2C%20and%20while%20people%20tend%20to%20appreciate%20money%20struggle%20stories%2C%20sharing%20money%20wins%20can%20be%20met%20with%20calls%20of%20being%20out%20of%20touch%2C%20privileged%2C%20and%20tone%20deaf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20seems%20to%20be%20different%2C%20though%2C%20Varbanova%20added%2C%20because%20it's%20TikTok%20who%20stands%20to%20lose%20out%20if%20people%20can%20pay%20off%20their%20debts%20with%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20banding%20together%20against%20the%20big%20man%2C%20TikTok%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BTikTok%20is%20this%20big%20billion-dollar%20corporation%3B%20let's%20take%20its%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20that%20while%20it's%20effective%20now%2C%20she%20isn't%20convinced%20the%20trend%20will%20last%20or%20that%20the%20strategy%20will%20work%20as%20a%20long-term%20means%20of%20paying%20off%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20risks%2C%20such%20as%20people%20having%20to%20set%20aside%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20earnings%20for%20taxes%20or%20having%20their%20content%20flagged%20by%20troll%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20too%20many%20community%20guideline%20violations%20will%20have%20you%20removed%20from%20the%20program%20with%20very%20little%20warning%20or%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20Brown%20said.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20pass%20go%3B%20do%20not%20collect%20%24200.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-new-gofundme-views-replacing-donations-debt-tiktokers-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716393281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664db9759fc063e829b3880c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-new-gofundme-views-replacing-donations-debt-tiktokers-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3Bpay%20off%20each%20other's%20debt%26quot%3B%20trend%20is%20taking%20off%20on%20TikTok%2C%20with%20people%20offering%20views%20and%20engagement%20on%20each%20other's%20videos%20to%20help%20boost%