took%20place%20around%202.15%20am%2C%20when%20the%20teenager%2C%20who%20had%20been%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20in%20two%20pubs%20in%20Pune%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results%2C%20knocked%20down%20the%20two%2024-year-old%20IT%20professionals%20in%20the%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area%20in%20the%20Rs%202.5-crore%20Porsche.%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20the%20bike%20was%20sent%20flying%20and%20hit%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20while%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20-%20who%20was%20riding%20pillion%20-%20was%20flung%2020%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%20Both%20of%20them%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2017%20years%20and%208%20months%20old%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20four%20months%20short%20of%20the%20legal%20age%20for%20driving.%20The%20legal%20drinking%20age%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%2025%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Pune%20Police%20Commissioner%20Amitesh%20Kumar%20had%20said%20the%20teenager%20had%20the%20knowledge%20that%20his%20act%20could%20cause%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20we%20are%20not%20applying%20a%20case%20of%20304(a)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20of%20drunken%20driving%20and%20a%20rash%20and%20negligent%20act.%20We%20are%20applying%20Section%20304%2C%20where%20we%20are%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20the%20knowledge%20that%20his%20rash%20act%20-%20where%20he%20was%20driving%20a%20Porsche%20without%20a%20number%20plate%20at%20a%20rash%20speed%20on%20a%20narrow%20street%20after%20consuming%20alcohol%20-%20could%20cause%20or%20was%20likely%20to%20cause%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFather%20In%20Custody%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20Pune%20teenager%20had%20been%20remanded%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20two%20days%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20realtor%20had%20been%20charged%20under%20Sections%2075%20(wilful%20neg