.%20She%20was%20the%20first%20to%20play%20cricket%20with%20neighbourhood%20boys%20and%20run%20for%20cover%20when%20her%20mother%20came%20looking%20for%20her.%20She%20made%20sure%20her%20soft%20voice%20wasn't%20lost%20in%20a%20room%20full%20of%20noise%2C%20and%20she%20was%20bold%20enough%20to%20say%20no%20to%20an%20early%20marriage%2C%20Ms%20Taukari%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20she%20influenced%20her%20family%20to%20let%20her%20make%20her%20own%20educational%20choices.%20At%20the%20age%20of%2019%2C%20she%20travelled%20for%20an%20internship%20outside%20her%20hometown%2C%20and%20by%2021%20she%20moved%20to%20Mumbai.%20She%20challenged%20herself%20academically%2C%20studying%20at%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20toughest%20communication%20schools%20even%20when%20many%20at%20home%20believed%20it%20was%20all%20too%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20small-town%20girlies%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwoman-takes-plane-seat-upgrade-and-leaves-ex-with-his-son-after-breakup-internet-defends-her-5721019%5C%22%3EWoman%20Takes%20Plane%20Seat%20Upgrade%20And%20Leaves%20Ex%20With%20His%20Son%20After%20Breakup%2C%20Internet%20Defends%20Her%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Taukari%20shared%20that%20her%20professional%20journey%20included%20working%20at%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20PR%20firms%2C%20pausing%20a%20promising%20career%20to%20reorganise%20her%20life%2C%20and%20taking%202.5%20years%20to%20focus%20on%20learning%2C%20volunteering%2C%20and%20living%20on%20her%20terms.%20She%20then%20packed%20up%20and%20moved%20to%20a%20different%20country%2C%20returned%20to%20university%20as%20a%20working%20woman%2C%20and%20didn't%20give%20up%20even%20when%20her%20experience%20was%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20the%20first%20to%20do%20anything%2C%20anywhere%20is%20very%20scary.%20To%20be%20the%20first%20doesn't%20mean%20to%20be%20perfect.%2