ether%20it's%20a%20pack%20of%20water%20or%20carrying%20groceries%20up%20the%20stairs%20into%20an%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20buy%20S-hooks%20that%20I%20use%20to%20hang%20bags%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20shopping%20carts%20as%20I%20shop.%20That%20way%2C%20I%20extend%20the%20capacity%20of%20one%20cart%20instead%20of%20having%20to%20get%20two%20carts%20when%20I'm%20shopping%20large%20orders%20or%20multiple%20orders%20at%20once.%20I%20also%20color-code%20the%20bags%20with%20clips%20to%20keep%20items%20for%20different%20orders%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22270e5ed6-d492-4745-a84a-b487c45248c8%5C%22%3EFigure%20out%20what%20the%20best%20times%20and%20places%20to%20shop%20are%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20area%2C%20I%20find%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%20is%20when%20orders%20start%20coming%20in.%20There%20are%20larger%20orders%20that%20are%20usually%20bigger%20tips%20or%20better%20pay.%20So%2C%20if%20you're%20a%20morning%20person%20and%20that's%20the%20time%20you're%20available%2C%20get%20up%2C%20sign%20on%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20you're%20close%20to%20one%20of%20your%20favorite%20stores%20or%20one%20that%20is%20in%20a%20good%20neighborhood%20that%20typically%20has%20good%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20affluent%20neighborhoods%20are%20not%20always%20the%20best%20tippers.%20Middle-class%20people%20are%20very%20grateful%20and%20often%20tip%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226194db8c-83ad-4068-bde4-c1679cb0f37a%5C%22%3ELook%20at%20the%20details%20of%20an%20order%20and%20be%20quick%20to%20claim%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20orders%20disappear%20quickly%20before%20you%20can%20even%20figure%20out%20whether%20you%20want%20it.%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20quick%20about%20figuring%20out%20how%20many%20miles%20it%20is%2C%20how%20much%20it%20pays%2C%20and%20how%20much%20the%20tip%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPick%20the%20orders%20that%20meet%20your%20needs%20and%20the%20time%20that%20you%20have%20available%20to%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20something%20that%20you%20weren't%20prepared%20for.%20Some%20orders%20say%20they're%20just%20six%20items%2C%20but%20if%20you%20look%20closer%2C%20you'll%20see%20it's%20actually%20dozens%20of%20%26quot%3Bunits%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20means%20the%20customer%20has%20ordered%20lots%20of%20the%20same%20item.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20deliver%20hundreds%20of%20pounds%20of%20San%20Pellegrino%20water%20from%20Costco%2C%20don't%20take%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8c7d28b-1b25-4e9f-b62d-0a6315da2b56%5C%22%3EDecide%20what%20you're%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20of%20shopping%20for%20Instacart%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20need%20the%20work%20to%20subsidize%20your%20income%2C%20you%20could%20deliver%20little%20orders%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20week%20before%20you%20go%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20your%20main%20source%20of%20income%2C%20you%20need%20to%20recognize%20that%20and%20plan%20for%20it.%20The%20pay%20and%20tips%20for%20some%20batches%20are%20much%20lower%20than%20others%2C%20so%20you%20need%20to%20know%20how%20to%20leverage%20Instacart%20to%20meet%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAn%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bshoppers%20may%20acquire%20whatever%20tools%20they%20would%20like%20to%20support%20their%20work.%26quot%3B%20Shoppers%20can%20verify%20their%20insulated%20bags%20through%20the%20Instacart%20app%20to%20get%20access%20to%20more%20batches%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Instacart%2C%20DoorDash%2C%20Walmart%20Spark%2C%20or%20another%20gig%20delivery%20service%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20art