flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hospital%20in%20Bangkok%20said%20Wednesday%20its%20staff%20were%20treating%2C%20or%20had%20treated%2085%20of%20those%20injured%2C%20including%2020%20people%20who%20were%20currently%20in%20intensive%20care%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020%20were%20from%20Australia%2C%20Britain%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Singapore%20and%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Samitivej%20hospital%20said%2C%20without%20specifying%20how%20many%20were%20passengers%20or%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20relief%20flight%20carrying%20131%20passengers%20and%2012%20crew%20landed%20at%20Singapore's%20Changi%20Airport%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelieved%20relatives%20greeted%20the%20arrivals%20with%20hugs%2C%20but%20all%20were%20too%20shaken%20to%20talk%20to%20waiting%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Davies%2C%20a%20British%20passenger%20aboard%20the%20Boeing%20777-300ER%2C%20told%20BBC%20radio%20that%20the%20plane%20%26quot%3Bsuddenly%20dropped%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20little%20warning%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20few%20seconds%20of%20the%20plane%20dropping%2C%20there%20was%20an%20awful%20screaming%20and%20what%20sounded%20like%20a%20thud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20helped%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20%26quot%3Bscreaming%20in%20agony%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bgash%20on%20her%20head%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20he%20told%20a%20BBC%20podcast%20he%20feared%20the%20plane%20was%20going%20to%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemembering%20the%20plane%20now%20--%20the%20huge%20dents%20in%20the%20roof%20that%20people%20had%20obviously%20hit%20with%20their%20head.%20There%20was%20a%20water%20bottle%20stuck%20in%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20ceiling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Airlines%20chief%20executive%20Goh%20Choon%20Phong%20said%20Wednesday%20the%20carrier%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20sorry%20for%20the%20traumatic%20experience%26quot%3B%20endured%20by%20those%20on%20board%2C%20and%20expressed%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Crazy%20flight'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Prime%20Minister%20Lawrence%20Wong%20sent%20his%20%26quot%3Bdeepest%20condolences%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20family%20and%20loved%20ones%20of%20the%20dead%20man%20--%20identified%20as%20Geoff%20Kitchen%2C%20a%20musical%20theatre%20director%20from%20near%20Bristol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20city-state%20is%20sending%20investigators%20to%20Bangkok%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20and%20Wong%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20that%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bworking%20closely%20with%20Thai%20authorities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20passengers%2C%2056%20were%20Australian%2C%2047%20British%20and%2041%20Singaporean%2C%20according%20to%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaysia's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20nine%20of%20its%20nationals%20were%20hospitalised%2C%20including%20one%20in%20a%20critical%20but%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AFP%20photographer%20saw%20people%20in%20Singapore%20Airlines%20yellow%20vests%20entering%20the%20plane%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20it%20remained%20grounded%20in%20Bangkok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20exactly%20what%20happened%2C%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20tell.%20But%20I%20think%20passengers%20are%20too%20casual%20on%20board%20commercial%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20US-based%20aerospace%20safety%20expert%20Anthony%20Brickhouse%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20the%20captain%20turns%20off%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%2C%20people%20literally%20unbuckle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavies%2C%20the%20passenger%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20plane%20suddenly%20dropped%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20very%20moment%20a%20seatbelt%20sign%20came%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllison%20Barker%20told%20the%20BBC%20her%20son%20Josh%2C%20who%20was%20aboard%20the%20plane%2C%20texted%20her%20that%2