lection%20is%20spread%20over%20seven%20phases%2C%20its%20longest%20since%20the%20first%20general%20election%20of%201951-52.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20macro%20geopolitical%20uncertainty.%20The%20future%20of%20globalisation%20is%20not%20going%20the%20way%20the%20companies%20want%20it%20to%20go.%20Politics%20is%20inserting%20itself%20into%20the%20global%20marketplace.%20The%20wars%20are%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that.%20US%20China%20relations%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20it.%20US%20elections%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20that.%20And%20all%20four%20of%20those%20are%20not%20going%20well.%20None%20of%20them%20are%20being%20managed%20easily.%20And%20the%20pressures%20in%20all%20of%20these%20major%20issues%20are%20more%20negative.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20looks%20stable%20and%20consistent%20politically%20is%20the%20India%20election.%20Everything%20else%20is%20problematic%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bremmer%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Eurasia%20Group%2C%20a%20risk%20and%20research%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20NDTV%20Profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bremmer%20maintains%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%2073%2C%20seeking%20re-election%2C%20will%20most%20likely%20be%20back%20in%20office%20for%20a%20third%20term%20with%20the%20same%20numbers%20as%20he%20did%20in%202019.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20won%20303%20seats%20then.%20This%20time%20he%20aims%20to%20win%20370%20seats%20and%20with%20help%20from%20allies%20hopes%20to%20cross%20400.%20There%20are%20543%20seats%20in%20the%20lower%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Eurasia%20Group%20is%20pretty%20consistent%20with%20where%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20landed%20the%20last%20time%20around.%20So%20it's%20305%2C%20plus%20or%20minus%2010%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Bremmer%2C%20adding%20his%20interest%20in%20not%20in%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assessment%20ties%20in%20with%20poll%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor's%20prediction%20for%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20tally%20may%20hover%20around%20its%202019%20score%20of%20303%20or%20better%20than%20it%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%20told%20NDTV%2C%20underscoring%20that%20there%20is%20no%20widespread%20anger%20against%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20nor%20a%20clamour%20for%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20past%20five%20months%2C%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20assess%20the%20elections%2C%20it%20seems%20Modi-led%20BJP%20is%20returning.%20They%20may%20get%20the%20same%20numbers%20as%20last%20election%20or%20do%20slightly%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kishor%2C%20who%20crafted%20Mr%20Modi's%202014%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20closes%20on%20June%201.%20Five%20phases%20are%20over%2C%20two%20more%20remain.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20the%20largest%20democracy%20that%20is%20going%20to%20the%20ballot.%20India%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20with%20the%20smoothest%20transition.%20There's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20system.%20It%20is%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair%20and%20transparent.%20And%20Modi%20who%20has%20been%20in%20power%20now%20for%20two%20terms%20is%20almost%20certainly%20going%20to%20be%20in%20power%20for%20another%20term%20on%20the%20back%20of%20pretty%20strong%20economic%20performance%20and%20consistent%20reform.%20That%20is%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20a%20very%20stabilising%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Bremmer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716386520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffj40pq_pm-1200_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-election-only-thing-that-looks-stable-top-us-political-scientist-to-ndtv-5722069%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20the%20year%20of%20elections.%20India%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20six-w