ure%20they%20are%20working%20under%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20put%20pressure%20on%20courts%20to%20have%20him%20freed%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20put%20any%20pressure.%20But%20if%20the%20pressure%20is%20lifted%20from%20the%20judiciary%20then%20justice%20will%20start%20to%20be%20served%20fairly%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20cases%20against%20me%20are%20bogus.%20There%20is%20no%20money%20trail%20anywhere.%20Not%20a%20single%20paisa%20has%20been%20traced.%20If%20there%20was%20corruption%2C%20where%20has%20the%20money%20gone%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20On%20May%2010%2C%20he%20was%20released%20from%20Tihar%20Jail%20so%20he%20could%20join%20his%20party's%20campaign%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20to%20surrender%20on%20June%202%20---%20a%20day%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20have%20alleged%20that%20his%20bail%20amounts%20to%20special%20treatment%20--%20a%20comment%20the%20court%20has%20objected%20to.%20The%20judges%20who%20granted%20bail%20said%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Bnot%20made%20any%20exception%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20unexpected%20step%2C%20the%20top%20court%2C%20which%20was%20hearing%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20challenge%20to%20his%20arrest%2C%20also%20said%20it%20would%20hear%20his%20appeal%20for%20bail.%20While%20granting%20interim%20bail%20in%20the%20same%20hearing%2C%20the%20judges%20said%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%20Elections%20are%20%26quot%3Bvis%20viva%26quot%3B%20(life%20force)%20of%20a%20democracy%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20heads%20a%20national%20party%2C%20that%20he%20is%20not%20convicted%20and%20is%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20society%2C%20the%20judges%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20also%20put%20aside%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20argument%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20comment%20that%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20wins%2C%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20have%20to%20go%20back%20to%20jail%26quot%3B%20--%20is%20a%20contempt%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20former%20Deputy%20and%20close%20party%20colleague%20Manish%20Sisodia%20is%20still%20in%20jail.%20So%20is%20former%20minister%20Satyender%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716386100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2cmun6nc_arvind-kejriwal-1200_625x300_20_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-tihar-jail-india-bloc-will-free-judiciary-from-pressure-arvind-kejriwal-explains-wont-have-to-go-back-to-jail-comment-5721914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20the%20judiciary%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20pressure%26quot%3B%20it%20is%20facing.%20This%2C%20he%20added%2C%20will%20lead%20to%20his%20release%20from%20jail%20on%20June%205%2C%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-tihar-jail-india-bloc-will-free-judiciary-from-pressure-arvind-kejriwal-explains-wont-have-to-go-back-to-jail-comment-5721914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-tihar-jail-india-bloc-will-free-judiciary-from-pressure-arvind-kejriwal-explains-wont-have-to-go-back-to-jail-comment-5721914%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-supreme-court-tihar-jail-i