h%20the%20expert%20whereas%20Rs%20150%20for%20a%20field%20visit%2C%20which%20Manish%20says%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20market%20which%20charges%20Rs%20300-500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20has%20also%20designed%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20tags%20to%20monitor%20and%20trace%20the%20health%2C%20location%2C%20and%20movement%20of%20livestock.%20It%20also%20stores%20prescriptions%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260896%2Fodisha-balaram-sahu-free-doctor-treatment-cow-cattle-diseases-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisease%20history%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%20Of%20this%2C%20more%20than%201.7%20lakh%20are%20directly%20benefitting%20through%20teleconsultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20major%20health%20issues%20in%20livestock%20were%20productivity%20and%20difficulties%20in%20pregnancies%20owing%20to%20malnutrition.%20We%20provide%20herbal%20treatment%20that%20boosts%20suitable%20ovulation%20period%20in%20cattle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%