%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20was%20admitted%20to%20KD%20Hospital%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20with%20the%20reason%20undisclosed.%20Reports%20indicate%20he%20was%20hospitalized%20due%20to%20dehydration%20and%20later%20discharged.%20No%20official%20health%20update%20is%20available%2C%20and%20Red%20Chillies%20Entertainment%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20inquiries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-admitted-to-hospital-in-ahmedabad-discharged-report%2Farticleshow%2F110338661.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singapore%20Airlines%20Flight%20Flew%20Through%20Dangerous%20Zone%20%26quot%3BThat%20Pilots%20Fear%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20pilot%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Singapore%20Airlines%20flight%2C%20which%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20severe%20turbulence%20leading%20to%20the%20death%20of%20one%20passenger%2C%20could%20have%20hit%20an%20area%20called%20the%20Intertropical%20Convergence%20Zone%20(ICZ).%20According%20to%20NASA%20Earth%20Observatory%2C%20it%20is%20a%20region%20that%20circles%20the%20Earth%20near%20the%20equator%2C%20where%20the%20trade%20winds%20of%20the%20Northern%20and%20Southern%20hemisphere%20come%20together.%20Due%20to%20the%20intense%20heat%20of%20the%20Sun%20and%20warm%20water%20of%20the%20equator%20in%20this%20region%2C%20the%20humidity%20content%20is%20high.%20Aided%20by%20the%20convergence%20of%20the%20trade%20winds%2C%20the%20buoyant%20air%20rises.%20As%20the%20air%20rises%20it%20expands%20and%20cools%2C%20releasing%20the%20accumulated%20moisture%20in%20an%20almost%20perpetual%20series%20of%20thunderstorms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbig-lesson-from-singapore-airlines-turbulence-terror-buckle-up-5718212%5C%22%3EBig%20Lesson%20From%20Singapore%20Airlines%20Turbulence%20Terror%3A%20Buckle%20Up%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarco%20Chan%2C%20a%20former%20commercial%20pilot%20and%20lecturer%20in%20aviation%20at%20Buckinghamshire%20New%20University%2C%20said%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20pilots'%20options%20may%20have%20been%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20turbulence%20of%20such%20magnitude%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20the%20Singapore%20Airlines%20flight%20was%20navigating%20through%20difficult%20thunderstorms%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chan%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fairlines%2Fsingapore-airlines-flight-london-turbulence-death-injuries-c744b9db%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20(WSJ)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20explaining%20the%20notorious%20storm%20system%2C%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fmay%2F21%2Fwhat-causes-air-turbulence-and-how-worried-should-passengers-be%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BThunderstorms%20are%20prominently%20displayed%20on%20the%20pilots'%20navigation%20display%20-%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20completely%20circumvent%20the%20storm%20cluster%20as%20they%20can%20stretch%20well%20over%2050%20nautical%20miles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20turbulence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20phenomenon%20caused%20by%20meeting%20of%20air%20at%20different%20temperatures%2C%20pressure%20or%20velocity%2C%20where%20different%20wind%20patterns%20collide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20its%20dangerous%20form%20is%20the%20clear-air%20turbulence%2C%20which%20can%20take%20plane%20pilots%20by%20surprise%20and%20occur%20without%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20777%20jet%20of%20Singapore%20Airlines%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Thailand%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20deadly%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-was-geoffrey-kitchen-the-man-who-died-in-singapore-airlines-turbulance-5720080%5C%22%3EGeoffrey%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%2073-year-old%20British%20passenger%2C%20died%20likely%20due%20to%20a%20heart%20attack%20on%20flight%20SQ321%2C%20said%20Kittipong%20Kittikachorn%2C%20general%20manager%20of%20Suvarnabhumi%20Airport%20in%20Bangkok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2060%20passengers%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20May%2021%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Airlines%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20it%20is%20fully%20cooperating%20with%20relevant%20authorities%20in%20the%20investigation%2C%20adding%20that%20all%20the%20passengers%20were%20examined%20and%20treated%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716385080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6hmcjlj_singapore-airlines_625x300_22_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fintertropical-convergence-zone-singapore-airlines-flight-flew-through-dangerous-zone-that-pilots-fear-report-5721870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Boeing%20777%20jet%20of%20Singapore%20Airlines%20had%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Thailand%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20deadly%20turbulence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fintertropical-convergence-zone-singapore-airlines-flight-flew-through-dangerous-zone-that-pilots-fear-report-5721870%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fintertropical-convergence-zone-singapore-airlines-flight-flew-through-dangerous-zone-that-pilots-fear-report-5721870%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fintertropical-convergence-zone-singapore-airlines-flight-flew-through-dangerous-zone-that-pilots-fear-report-572