Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20judge%20is%20saying%2C%20'I%20am%20an%20RSS%20person'%2C%20another%20one%20joins%20the%20BJP%E2%80%A6%20How%20can%20you%20be%20a%20judge%20this%20way%20and%20preside%20over%20courts%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20party%20leader%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20also%20alleged%20the%20court's%20judgment%20is%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20efforts%20to%20cancel%20reservation%20for%20the%20Tapashili%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716384840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-05%2Foed03fo_calcutta-high-court-pti_625x300_28_May_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-cancels-caste-certificates-from-trinamool-government-5721000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20cancelled%20all%20certificates%20to%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20issued%20in%20Bengal%20since%202011%20under%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20administration%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-cancels-caste-certificates-from-trinamool-government-5721000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-cancels-caste-certificates-from-trinamool-government-5721000%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcalcutta-high-court-cancels-caste-certificates-from-trinamool-government-5721000%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shahid%2C%20Aishwarya%2C%20Rakul-Jackky%3A%20Top%205%20news%20of%20the%20day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716384600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110337283%2Cimgsize-35774.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshahid-k