%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%20Accused%20Of%20Beheading%20Dog%20He%20Adopted%20From%20Shelter%20One%20Day%20Earlier%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2066-year-old%20man%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20decapitating%20a%20pet%20dog%20that%20he%20had%20adopted%20from%20an%20animal%20shelter%20just%20one%20day%20earlier.%20In%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20the%20Pinellas%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office%20said%20that%20deputies%20began%20looking%20for%20Domingo%20Rodriguez%20on%2014%20May%2C%20after%20they%20received%20reports%20of%20a%20dead%20dog%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%20at%20a%20park%20in%20Florida.%20Officers%20were%20called%20to%20the%20scene%20where%20they%20found%20the%20dog%20without%20a%20head%20floating%20in%20a%20mangrove%20swamp%20in%20the%20park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20scanned%20the%20dog's%20microchip%20and%20identified%20it%20as%20being%20a%204-year-old%20bulldog%20mix.%20Deputies%20also%20discovered%20the%20animal%20had%20been%20adopted%20from%20Pinellas%20County%20Animal%20Services%20on%20May%2010%20by%20Domingo%20Rodriguez.%20Mr%20Rodriguez%2C%2066%2C%20has%20now%20been%20charged%20with%20one%20count%20of%20felony%20animal%20cruelty%20and%20one%20count%20of%20disposal%20of%20bodies%20of%20dead%20animals%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pinellas%20County%20Sheriff's%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeputies%20have%20arrested%2066-year-old%20Domingo%20Rodriquez%20and%20charged%20him%20with%20one%20count%20of%20Animal%20Cruelty%20and%20one%20count%20of%20Disposal%20of%20Bodies%20of%20Dead%20Animals%20after%20his%204-year-old%20bulldog%20mix%20named%20Dexter%20was%20found%20deceased%20at%20Ft.%20Desoto%20Park%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Facebook%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fpinellassheriff%252Fposts%252F