%203%20hours%20tending%20to%20her%20plants%20daily.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20start%20speaking%20till%20he%20was%20three%2C%20doctors%20assured%20them%20that%20it%20might%20be%20a%20speech%20delay%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20wait%20till%20four.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20initial%20few%20years%2C%20my%20son%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sleep%20for%20more%20than%20four%20hours.%20He%20also%20did%20not%20communicate.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20write%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20which%20led%20us%20to%20think%20that%20he%20had%20high%20IQ%20levels.%20The%20doctors%20also%20kept%20asking%20us%20to%20wait%20for%20another%20six%20months%20to%20one%20year%20for%20his%20speech%20to%20develop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sushma%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20continued%20till%20four%2C%20the%20concerned%20parents%20took%20him%20to%20different%20doctors%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20correct%20diagnosis%20of%20ADHD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20autism%2Ca%20neurological%20condition%20that%20causes%20difficulty%20with%20social%20interaction%20and%20communication%2C%20at%20the%20NIMHANS%20(National%20Institute%20of%20Mental%20Health%20and%20Neurosciences)%2C%20she%20shares%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20therapy%20for%20the%20same.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20therapy%20sessions%20and%20difficulty%20in%20communicating%20with%20her%20little%20one%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20young%20mother%2C%20which%20subsequently%20led%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20up%20gardening%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp