g%20wild%20biodiversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20while%20on%20a%20drive%2C%20Ganesh%20came%20across%20Saguna%20Baug%20and%20having%20heard%20so%20much%20about%20the%20place%2C%20decided%20to%20stop%20by.%20They%20say%20some%20things%20can%20change%20your%20life%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20completely.%20For%20Ganesh%2C%20a%20guided%20tour%20through%20the%20green%20space%20with%20Bhadsavle%E2%80%99s%20running%20commentary%20on%20how%20freeing%20nature%20could%20really%20be%20was%20one%20such%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20all%20I%20needed%20to%20confirm%20my%20faith%20in%20an%20idea%20that%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20vision%20finally%20got%20a%20name.%20He%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20agro-tourism%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20mangoes%20play%20host%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minute%20you%20step%20into%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20stark%20difference%20between%20the%20city%20air%20from%20the%20fresh%20gusts%20here.%20Mango%20trees%20move%20almost%20melodically%2C%20the%20branches%20causing%20a%20rustle%20that%20makes%20you%20stop%20and%20want%20to%20interpret.%20Watching%20these%20beauties%20and%20feasting%20on%20their%20fruits%20constitutes%20a%20great%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanesh%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20inception%20behind%20this%20homestay%20idea%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20once%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20packing%20unit.%20When%20we%20started%20getting%20so%20many%20guests%20visiting%20us%20to%20watch%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20practices%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20create%20a%20place%20where%20they%20could%20stay.%20And%20so%