%20well%2C%20given%20the%20temperature%20here%20rises%20to%2046%20degrees%20in%20the%20summer.%20But%20this%20challenge%20is%20what%20exactly%20makes%20it%20fun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20where%20he%20keeps%20new%20saplings%20for%202-3%20months%20to%20help%20them%20acclimatise.%20%E2%80%9CI%20introduce%20them%20to%20direct%20sunlight%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Miyazaki%20mango%20plant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20planted%20it%20directly%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20my%20house.%20Its%20sapling%20cost%20me%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20take%20any%20risk.%20I%20let%20the%20sapling%20settle%20into%20the%20soil.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20I%20added%20cow%20dung%2C%20bone%20meal%2C%20neem%20and%20mustard%20cakes%20to%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-i